{"tid":2245363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國全球數據中心選址浙江　專家質憂成中國情報網絡","createTime":"2020-10-16T07:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T10:01:35.000Z","uid":10717,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de0ccb0c52120d2d2c85a6019c54b5e5f73e05b4","tid":2245363,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"美國政府近年嚴阻中國手機程式、雲端服務商，阻止中國政府取得敏感數據。但聯合國秘書處最近卻與北京合作，在浙江省德清縣建立全球大的數據中心，以及利用衛星監視技術的「地理空間中心」，處理來自聯合國各成員國的數據。簽署數據中心協議的聯合國官員同樣來自中國，有專家憂慮數據中心會成為中國的全球情報網絡。<br />\n<br />\n數據中心中心選址浙江省德清縣的消息，最早由《華爾街日報》前記者、哈德遜研究所研究员 Claudia Rosett 在上周撰文披露。她批評，計劃根本是中國假借聯合國名義，加強監控範圍。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，浙江省德清曾於 2018 年舉辦聯合國世界地理空間信息大會，而當地距離杭州不到一個小時的車程，後者是中國科企巨頭阿里巴巴集團所在地，而該集團由中國首富馬雲創立。"},{"pid":"3c029e72471509db15422bf692701a6baa5eb9ec","tid":2245363,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"聯合國變成中國地頭"},{"pid":"1a5bf1b5d484ece27282866fc1c8005956359799","tid":2245363,"uid":35924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"聯合國已經有名冇實，班左膠國自食其果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4aebd83196f15d134bdbe64c95441555a1bcab","tid":2245363,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"聯合中國"},{"pid":"cda054592933063c2dbc3fd22dca4b080ef12872","tid":2245363,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"帶頭唔交data上去未得囉<br />\n<br />\n自己成立nato 加東盟 非盟 圈子"},{"pid":"158a48429c339c94adb75aae9bfcdb9366e62236","tid":2245363,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"國際聯盟2.0"},{"pid":"52e2205f7ebf4d965b4ee704544b5a7884f04021","tid":2245363,"uid":66949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"158a48429c339c94adb75aae9bfcdb9366e62236","tid":2245363,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"國際聯盟2.0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身就係國聯2.0<br />\n<br />\n唔同既係日本呢啲軸心國係自己退出<br />\n<br />\n支那就滲透哂入去"},{"pid":"09aeba9505becde85ddd7fa86c992b29fa3ea999","tid":2245363,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db666b8e512eeeb0a4c1e9245e4a995ff0c83f2a","tid":2245363,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Phusfn4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhusfn4.jpg&h=b4b3c7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗撚你 D 專家講咩，比共產黨入咗嘅聯合國重有撚用咩"}]}